Package: ggefp
Type: Package
Title: A way to plot tissue maps using ggplot2
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Henning Redestig <henning.red@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Henning Redestig <henning.red@gmail.com>
Description: Defines a ggplot2 geom that maps values to tissues in provided
    plant line drawings. Arabidopsis line drawing adapted from Winter et al.
    (2007) PLoS ONE 2(8): e718. doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0000718
Depends:
    methods,
    ggplot2
Imports:
    proto,
    grid,
    grImport,
    plyr
